ex":13,"publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67"},{"id":"2304da6444","type":"paragraph","text":"十年来，我们造反派同老狗们的斗争积累了许多的经验。你们天","index":14,"publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67"},{"id":"460616fe3a","type":"paragraph","text":"有你们的“老验”，我们有我们的“新验”，你们没有而我们有的是“朝气”，","index":15,"publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67"},{"id":"47123b09ec","type":"paragraph","text":"反动考力是不会自行退出历史舞台的，你们答应朱洪同志","index":16,"publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67"},{"id":"557b35d2df","type":"paragraph","text":"人党，把朱洪厦同志从城市搞到农村，再从乡下搞到城市，得好苦牙。朱、李、胡、吴都被你们整得够苦的，你们在宁央和广大群众的压力之下，好不容易才让出一条小路，共目的有你下三条：（1）把造反派的思想搞乱，分裂造尿派：（2）楚造反派混乱之机，静动静，待机反扑：（3）你们把一部分权力交给某些人，使他们上钩，袖手旁观，然后张弓拔箭，一箭双胜。我们要识","index":17,"publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67"},{"id":"8a3495babc","type":"paragraph","text":"破老狗们的阴谋。A","index":18,"publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67"},{"id":"9a50ff82fd","type":"paragraph","text":"读报有感（节录）","index":19,"publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67"},{"id":"8b9acecaed","type":"paragraph","text":"一从西哈劳克正体读起","index":20,"publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67"},{"id":"b7d10250ff","type":"paragraph","text":"吴仁花","index":21,"publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67"},{"id":"77ee817a4c","type":"paragraph","text":"四月X日，《人民日报》刊载一条消息，民主京塘筹政府批准","index":22,"publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67"}],"page":{"id":"a21c52464d","publicationId":"982b2747-bdfb-4011-9441-73f04bf9b94f","articleId":"9156187e67","start":5,"end":6}}}},"__N_SSG":true}